show.description: Ex-wife ke heartbreak se leke CEO ke love trap tak — Kate ki life hai full drama, betrayal aur unexpected romance se! Kya 3-month ki fake marriage sach mein uski life badal degi? Dekhiye ye rollercoaster journey jahan har episode mein twist guaranteed hai.
